@startuml traffic-flow-cold-start
!include ../../datum-theme-sequence.puml

participant "OVS Bridge" as ovs
participant "Wake Daemon" as daemon
participant "Instance" as instance

note over ovs: Packet arrives for\nsleeping instance.\nNo matching flow rule.

ovs -> daemon: Flow miss\n(packet for sleeping instance)

== Boot Instance (~3-14ms) ==

daemon -> instance: Wake instance\n(runtime wake API)

instance --> daemon: Ready signal

== Release Traffic ==

daemon -> ovs: Install flow rule\nfor instance
ovs -> instance: Release held packet\nvia TAP

note over ovs, instance: Subsequent packets match\nOVS flow rule, offloaded\nto DPU eSwitch hardware.

note right of daemon: Total cold-start latency:\n3-14ms (boot time only).\nClient never retransmits.

@enduml
